API_KEY comes from process.env.AURA_API_KEY (line 161). The `===` short-circuits on first differing byte, making comparison time a function of the matching prefix length — a timing oracle in principle. Rate limiters at lines 140/143-156 and network jitter make practical remote exploitation unlikely, hence low severity.
